messageValues.message:
=Using the following JSON data about Nike:

{
  "search_term": "Nike",
  "knowledge_panel": {
    "name": "Nike",
    "label": "Company",
    "description": {
      "text": "Nike Inc. is an American multinational corporation founded in 1964 and officially named in 1971, engaged in the design, development, manufacturing, and worldwide marketing and sales of sportswear, footwear, and equipment. Headquarters in Beaverton, Oregon.",
      "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nike,_Inc.",
      "site": "Wikipedia"
    },
    "info": [
      {"title": "CEO", "labels": ["John Donahoe (since Jan 13, 2020)"]},
      {"title": "Founded", "labels": ["January 25, 1964, Eugene, Oregon"]},
      {"title": "Founders", "labels": ["Philip Knight", "Bill Bowerman"]},
      {"title": "Revenue", "labels": ["$37.4 billion USD"]},
      {"title": "Headquarters", "labels": ["Beaverton, Oregon"]}
    ]
  }
}

Create:
1. A short brand overview (max 3 sentences).
2. 5 creative social media post ideas for Nike’s Instagram, each with engaging captions.
3. A one-week content plan for Instagram including type of post (image, video, reel, story), main topic, and caption idea.
4. A list of 10 trending hashtags relevant to Nike.

